Package: armbian-web-config
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, python3, python3-flask, network-manager, sudo, cracklib-runtime
Description: Web-based initial setup tool for Armbian
 This package provides a browser-based counterpart to armbian-firstlogin,
 allowing users to easily configure their device over an access point.
